## 1. Scientific Repositories & Preprints

| Resource | Description | URL |
|----------|-------------|-----|
| **arXiv.org** | Free preprint server for STEM fields | https://arxiv.org/ |
| **bioRxiv** | Biology preprints | https://www.biorxiv.org/ |
| **medRxiv** | Health sciences preprints | https://www.medrxiv.org/ |
| **ChemRxiv** | Chemistry preprints | https://chemrxiv.org/ |
| **PsyArXiv** | Psychology preprints | https://psyarxiv.com/ |
| **SocArXiv** | Social sciences preprints | https://osf.io/preprints/socarxiv/ |
| **Zenodo** | General research data and DOIs | https://zenodo.org/ |
| **CORE** | Open access aggregator | https://core.ac.uk/ |
| **EarthArXiv** | Geoscience preprints | https://eartharxiv.org/ |
| **marXiv** | Materials science preprints | https://www.marxiv.org/ |
| **AfricArXiv** | African-focused preprints | https://info.africarxiv.org/ |
| **SciELO** | Latin American open access journals | https://scielo.org/ |
| **OpenDOAR** | Directory of Open Access Repositories | https://v2.sherpa.ac.uk/opendoar/ |
| **DOAPR** | Directory of Open Access Preprint Repositories | https://doapr.coar-repositories.org/ |

