| **UMA** | Universal Model for Atoms (Meta, May 2025) | https://ai.meta.com/research/publications/uma-a-family-of-universal-models-for-atoms/ |
| **Qiskit** | Open quantum SDK (IBM) | https://qiskit.org/ |
| **PennyLane** | Quantum ML library (Xanadu) | https://pennylane.ai/ |
| **LiveCodeBenchPro** | Advanced coding benchmark for LLM evaluation (June 2025) | https://livecodebenchpro.com/ |
| **OWASP Top 10 for LLMs** | Critical security vulnerabilities in LLM applications | https://owasp.org/www-project-top-10-for-large-language-model-applications/ |
| **MITRE ATLAS** | Knowledge base for adversarial tactics against ML systems | https://atlas.mitre.org/ |

