## 🔄 Recent Updates

### Version 2.3 (October 2025)

**✅ Verified & Corrected:**
- OMol25 (now with correct Hugging Face URL)
- UMA (now with correct Meta AI URL)
- FAIR² (description updated, correct Frontiers URL)
- LiveCodeBenchPro (verified and URL added)

**➕ New Additions:**
- OpenDOAR & DOAPR (directories)
- NASA OSDR (spaceflight data)
- Globus, DMPTool, LabArchives, REDCap (research data management)
- OWASP Top 10 for LLMs & MITRE ATLAS (LLM security)

**❌ Removed:**
- REACH (NOAA) – no evidence of existence
- Lock-LLMs – replaced with established security frameworks

**📂 New Section:**
- Research Data Management Platforms

### Previous Versions

- **v2.2 (Oct 2025):** Added Altmetric, Papers with Code, EleutherAI, SciELO, Plan S, CLOCKSS, Portico, workflow visualization
- **v2.1 (Oct 2025):** Original comprehensive compilation
- **v2.0 and earlier:** Initial development

