If you use this toolkit in your research or teaching, please cite it as:

```bibtex
@misc{opensciencetoolkit2025,
  title={The Open Science Toolkit: A Comprehensive Guide to Open Research \& Knowledge Preservation},
  author={{Open Science Toolkit Contributors}},
  version={2.3},
  year={2025},
  month={October},
  url={https://github.com/yourusername/open-science-toolkit},
  note={DOI to be assigned via Zenodo}
}
```

**APA Style:**
Open Science Toolkit Contributors. (2025). *The Open Science Toolkit: A Comprehensive Guide to Open Research & Knowledge Preservation* (Version 2.3). https://github.com/yourusername/open-science-toolkit

